# =============================================================================
# .dockerignore — NanoXplore RH
#
# Excludes files that must NOT be copied into the Docker build context.
# Keeping the context lean = faster builds and smaller images.
#
# Rule of thumb: if it isn't needed to `npm ci` + `npm run build` + run the
# server, it should be listed here.
# =============================================================================

# ── Dependencies (reinstalled inside the image) ───────────────────────────────
# Explicite ET glob — certaines versions de BuildKit ignorent le ** sur les sous-dossiers
node_modules
client/node_modules
server/node_modules
**/node_modules
**/npm-debug.log*
**/package-lock.json.bak

# ── Build outputs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/dist
server/public          # generated by `vite build` — rebuilt inside Docker
client/.vite

# ── Environment & secrets (NEVER bake into the image) ────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example          # .env.example is safe to include (no real secrets)

# ── Git ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# ── Infrastructure files (not needed at runtime inside the container) ─────────
nginx/
scripts/
database/              # init.sql is mounted as a volume, not baked in
docker-compose*.yml
Dockerfile*            # no need to copy Dockerfiles into themselves

# ── TLS certificates (mounted as volumes at runtime) ─────────────────────────
nginx/certs

# ── Logs ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
logs/

# ── Tests & coverage ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/__tests__
**/*.test.js
**/*.spec.js
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output

# ── Documentation ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
README.md
CHANGELOG.md
LICENSE
docs/

# ── Editor & OS artefacts ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
